ProductName: Mens Union Glashuette Belisar Moonphase Automatic Chronograph Watch
Description: Classic watchmaking excellence from Union Glashutte, this Belisar Moonphase features a finely decorated self winding automatic chronograph movement visible through the exhibition case back, featuring an annual calendar, 24 hour dial and moonphase as well as 60 hour power reserve, displayed in an elegant, sophisticated fashion using day pointer and dial windows, on a pure white dial with crisp applied rose numerals and blued hands.
